尊敬的新老朋友:</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="mso-char-indent-count: 1.0"><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 15pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
大家好!</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="mso-char-indent-count: 1.0"><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 15pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>&nbsp;
<span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 15pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
自我公布了婚讯，我的邮箱里收到了很多新老朋友各种的祝福和要求回信的留言。其中也有一些外国媒体的朋友，鉴于本人身体状态不宜太劳累，所以无法一一联系。待我顺利产下麟儿身体康复后会与一些真诚的朋友联络。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="mso-char-indent-count: 1.0"><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 15pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;再次感谢新老朋友的关心并祝愿你们万事顺利!</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="MArGin-LeFT: 352.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -23.5">
